    <p><b>1. <u>Introduction</u></b><br>
      Welcome to Neonova! These policies outline how your data is stored and used across our bot. By using Neonova, you agree to the following terms regarding data collection, storage, and usage.<br><br>

      <b>2. <u>Data Storage and Usage (Users)</u></b><br>
      Neonova stores your username and Discord user ID for the main functionality of the bot. By using Neonova, you consent to this data collection and storage.<br><br>

      <b>3. <u>Data Storage and Usage (Guilds)</u></b><br>
