      <b>4. <u>Neonova's Security</u></b><br>
      We implement a variety of security measures to protect your personal information when you place an order, submit data, or access your information. However, please note that our storage systems are not 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.<br><br>

      <b>5. <u>Data Deletion</u></b><br>
      Personal data is stored only for as long as necessary for the purposes for which it was collected. If you would like to request the deletion of your data, you can do so by contacting us. Please note that abuse of the data deletion system may result in a ban from our contact form.<br><br>
